metadata.name: Golden Ape #2
metadata.description: Golden Ape is a handcrafted collection of rare and beautiful NFTs created by artist @Landlord, powered by Ethereum. Golden Ape is the genesis collection of an ever-evolving ecosystem consisting Golden Ape Collection and much more. Deep dive into the Golden Ape Ecosystem of limitless possibilities and earn rewards such as Ecosystem NFTs & Coins, Merchandise and much more!
